Sainsbury's uhlela kukhula kuya e-UK beauty market
ISainsbury's itsi Boots, Superdrug kanye neDebenhams balwa netindzawo tekuhlobisa letitfolakala esitolo lesisebentisa tisebenti letisebentako.
Njengencenye yekwandziswa lokukhulu kwemakethe yebuhle yase-UK lengu-£2.8 billion, lechubeka nekukhula ngesikhatsi kutsengiswa kwetintfo tekugcoka kanye netekwakha ekhaya kwehla, letitolo letinkhulu letisetitolo letingu-11 eveni lonkhe titawuvivinywa futsi uma ngabe tiphumelela, titawuhanjiswa tiye etitolo letinyenti kulomnyaka lotako.
Kutsenga imali ebuhleni kwenteka njengobe tindlu letinkhulu tifuna tindlela tekugcwalisa ema-shelf labekadzeni asetjentiswa kuma-TV, ema-microwave kanye netintfo tekwakha.
Sainsbury's utsi itawuphindza kabili umkhicito wayo wetitfombe letitfolakalako kute kube ngu-3 000 futsi itawufaka emabito lafaka ekhatsi Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman kanye naDokotela PawPaw.
