Ngetulu kwaloko, sitolo setintfo letiyinkhanuko, i-Fragrance Shop, sitawuhlola kutsi kunetintfo letitsini letitfolakala ku-Sainsbury's, lesinye saletfolakala e-Croydon, eNingizimu London, futsi lesinye sitawutfolakala e-Selly Oak, eBirmingham, ngalelinye lilanga kulomnyaka.
Kutsenga ngetindlela te-Internet kanye nekutsenga kudla lokuncane lokutsengwa njalo nje etitolo letitsengisa tintfo letincane, kusho kutsi tikhulu kufanele tentisise kute tikholise bantfu kutsi batovakashela.
Mike Coupe, longumphatsi lomkhulu weSainsbury's, watsi letitolo titawuba tifanana netitolo letincane njengobe lelisuphamakethe yetama kuhlasela titolo letitfolakalako letingu-Aldi naLidl ngetinsita letinyenti kanye netintfo letingafani netekudla.
Sainsbury's ibeke ema-Argos emakhulwini etitolo futsi yenta letinye tintfo letitsite letitwa ngekutsi yi-Habitat kusukela yatsenga letinketane eminyakeni lemibili leyendlulile, lokusho kutsi loko kwente kutsi kutsengiswa kwetintfo tekudla kucinise futsi kwenta kutsenga kube nenzuzo.
Umzamo wekuvuselela tindzawo tekwenta tintfo letimnandzi kanye netitolo tekugcoka wehluleka.
Sainsbury's wacala kusebenta ndzawonye naBoots ngemnyaka wa 2000 kepha lobudlelwano baphela ngemuva kwekuphikisana ngekutsi inzuzo levela kumakhemisi kumele ihlukaniswe njani emkhatsini wetitolo tayo.
Lendlela lensha yavela ngemuva kwekutsi Sainsbury's eminyakeni lemitsatfu leyendlulile itsengise ibhizinisi yayo yema-apotheki letitolo letingu-281 ku-Celesio, umnikati we-Lloyds Pharmacy, ngemali lengetulu kwa- £125m.
Loku kusho kutsi iLloyds itawuba nendzima kuloluhlelo ngekuniketa luhlelo lolukhulu lwetintfo tekunakekela sikhumba, lokufaka ekhatsi iLa Roche-Posay neVichy, etitolo letine.
Paul Mills-Hicks, longumcondzisi wetekuhweba eSainsbury's, watsi: "Sishintje indlela lebukeka ngayo kanye nendlela lesicabanga ngayo ngetindlela tetfu tekuhlobisa kute sente imvelo ibe ncono kumakhasimende etfu.
