I-US Kumele Iphindze Kabili Imali Yekuceceshwa Kwema-AI
Njengobe iChina seyitfutfukisa buhlakani lobucinile, i-US kufanele iphindvwe kabili imali leseyitsatsa kucwaninga, kusho umtshali wetimali kanye nemuntfu losebenta ngekuhlakanipha kwebuchwephesha (AI) Kai-Fu Lee, losebenta ku-Google, Microsoft kanye ne-Apple.
Letincomo tivela ngemuva kwekutsi tincenye letinyenti tahulumende waseMelika setente tincwadzi letitsi AI, ngisho noma i-USA ingakatsatsi sikhatsi lesidze kutsi isungule lisu lelisemtsetfweni le-AI.
Ngaleyo ndlela, eChina ngemnyaka lowengcile, yatisa luhlelo lwayo lwekutsi nga-2030, ibe nguNombolo 1 yetintfo letentiwa nge-AI.
Lee watsi: "Kuphindzaphindza kabili imali yetinhlelo tekucwaninga nge-AI kutawuba sicalekiso lesihle, uma sicabanga kutsi onkhe lamanye emave asele kakhulu eMelika futsi sesibheke embili kulokuchutjwa kwe-AI lokulandzelako".
Kuphindvwe kabili kwetimali kungenta kube matima kakhulu kutsi umuntfu atfole umsebenti lomkhulu we-AI eMelika, kusho Lee ku-CNBC kuleliviki.
Lee, lonencwadzi letsi "AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" leyabhalwa nguHoughton Mifflin Harcourt kulenyanga, nguye loyinhloko yeSinovation Ventures, lofake imali ku-Face++, yinye yetinkampani letihamba embili te-AI eChina.
Nga-1980s e-Carnegie Mellon University, wasebenta eluhlelweni lwe-AI lolwaphumelela kakhulu emdlalweni we-Othello waseMelika, futsi muva waba sikhulu se-Microsoft Research kanye nemengameli we-China ye-Google.
Lee wavuma emncintiswaneni wetikhungo tebucwepheshe lobewentiwa nguhulumende waseMelika, njengenchabhayi ye-Robotics ye-Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency, futsi wabuta kutsi kutawuba nini lomncintiswano lolandzelako kute asite ekuboneni lombono lolandzelako.
Lee watsi bacwaningi base-US bavame kudzingeka basebente kamatima kute batfole imali yahulumende.
Lee watsi: "Loku akusiko lokutawutsatsa baholi betemfundvo baseChina; lokutawutsatsa emabhizinisi".
Kuleminyaka leyendlulile, i-Facebook, i-Google kanye naletinye tinkampani letisebenta ngeticwepheshe, batfole bantfu labanemandla lavela kuletinye tinhlangano temfundvo lephakeme kutsi basebente ku-AI.
Lee utsi tingucuko temgomo wekufika eveni nato tingasita ekuciniseni imitamo ye-AI yaseMelika.
"Ngicabanga kutsi emakhadi laluhlata kufanele atfunyelwe ngekutitsandzela kubantfu labaphenyako ku-AI", washo.
NgaJuly 2017, i-China State Council ikhiphe luhlelo lwayo lwekutfutfukiswa kwe-Artificial Intelligence.
Li-National Science Foundation yaseChina iniketa timali kubantfu labasemakhosini, ngendlela lefanako naleyo leentiwa yi-National Science Foundation naletinye tinhlangano tahulumende kutsi tinikete bacwaningi baseMelika imali, kodvwa lizinga lemsebenti we-academic eChina liyaphansi, kusho Lee.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, Litiko Letekutekulwa laseMelika lasungula sikhungo lesihlanganyelwe sekucwaninga ngekucwaninga lokufakelwa lokuhloswe ngaso kutsi sihlanganyele balingani labasemkhakheni kanye netemfundvo, futsi i-White House imemezele kusungulwa kwelikomidi lekuhlola ngekucwaninga lokufakelwa.
Kulenyanga le-DARPA imemezele kutsatsa imali lengu-R2 billion ku-AI Next.
I-NSF itsatsa imali lengetulu kwetigidzi letingu-100 ngemnyaka ekucwaningeni nge-AI.
Ngalesikhatsi, emitsetfo yaseMelika lebeyifuna kwakha liKomidi Lelikhombisa Kuthula (i-Artificial Intelligence) yacala kubhidlitwa etinyangeni letendlulile.
