I-Greece, lelineSifundza lesitsiwa yiMacedonia, iyachubeka itsi libito lelikhashane nayo lese nyakatfo limele kutsi ibambe leligama futsi iyala kubandlululwa e-NATO nase-EU.
NgaJune, bohulumende lababili bakhetsa kuvumelana ngelibito lelisha lebelibekiwe, kodvwa baphikisi betive batsi loko kutawenta kutsi bantfu baseMasedoniya labatiwako babe bete buntfu lobuhle.
