Bantfu labafuna kugucula libito, lokufaka ekhatsi Ndvunankhulu Zoran Zaev, batsi loko kuyinhlawulo lekhokhwa ngekucitsa sikhatsi sekwemukelwa kweMakedoniya, lenye yalamave lavela ekuweni kweYugoslavia, kuletinye tikhungo letifana ne-EU ne-NATO.
