"Ngilapha kutewuvota ngenca yebantfwana bami, indzawo yetfu iseYurophu", kwasho Gjose Tanevski, loneminyaka lengu-62, lovota enhlokodolobha iSkopje.
EM yaseMacedonia, Zoran Zaev, umkakhe Zorica kanye nendvodzana yakhe Dushko, bavota ku-referendum yaseMacedonia mayelana nekuguculwa kwelibito lelitolela live kutsi lijoyine i-NATO ne-European Union, eStrumica, eMacedonia, mhla ti-30 Septemba 2018.
Phambi kwephalamende yaseSkopje, Vladimir Kavardarkov, loneminyaka lengu-54, walungiselela umhlangano lomncane futsi wasusa tihlalo emathendeni labekwe ngulabo labatawuyekela kucocisana.
