John Edward: Emakhono elulwimi abalulekile kubantfu bemhlaba wonkhe
Tikolwa letitimele taseScotland tinemphumelelo lenkhulu kakhulu etemfundvweni, futsi nga-2018 kwachubeka nalenye inombolo lenkhulu yemiphumela yekuhlola, leyentiwa ibe ncono kakhulu ngemphumelelo yebantfu ngamunye kanye neyekuhlanganyela kutemidlalo, kutemacembu, umculo kanye naletinye tinhlangano temphakatsi.
Letikolwa, letimelelwa nguMkhandlu Wetifundvo Letitimele WaseScotland (SCIS), tinetisebenti letingetulu kwa-30,000 eScotland, tifuna kuniketa bafundzi babo kanye nebatali babo litfuba lelihle lekubafundzisa.
Tikhungo letitimele temfundvo tinenjongo yekulungiselela bafundzi babo kutsi batfole imfundvo lephakeme, umsebenti labakhetsile kanye nesimo sabo sekuba takhamuti temhlaba.
Njengemkhakha wemfundvo longahle ukhiphe futsi usebentise luhlelo lwemfundvo lolungentelwe etikolweni, sibona tilwimi temhlaba wonkhe tichubeka tiyincenye ledzingekako etikolweni.
Nelson Mandela watsi: "Nawukhuluma nemuntfu ngelulwimi lalicondza, uya ekhanda lakhe.
Nangabe ukhuluma naye ngelulwimi lwakhe, loko kuya enhlitiyweni yakhe".
Lesikhumbuzo lesinemandla kutsi singeke setsembele esiNgisini kuphela nangabe sifuna kwakha budlelwane nekwetsemba nebantfu bakulamanye emave.
Ngemiphumela yalamuhla yaleminyaka lemibili, sibona kutsi tilwimi tiphakeme kakhulu etitfulweni tetikolo letitimele.
Bantfu labatifundzisako labatfola tifundvo ngetilwimi letingasilo tabo, labangu-68 ekhulwini, batfola tifundvo letingaba ngu-A.
Idatha lebutfwe etikolweni letingu-74 te-SCIS ikhombise kutsi bafundzi labangu-72 ekhulwini batfola tigaba letingu-A ngesiMandarin, kantsi bafundzi labangu-72 ekhulwini labafundza siJalimane, labangu-69 bebafundza siFrench, kanye nalababangu-63 bebafundza siSpanish nabo batfola tigaba letingu-A.
Loku kukhombisa kutsi tikolwa letitimele taseScotland tisekela tilwimi letingesito letitawudzingeka kubantfwana nakubantfu labasha esikhatsini lesitako.
Tilwimi nyalo setibaluleke kakhulu njengetifundvo letitsatfwa njengetifundvo letitsite njengetifundvo letitsi STEM (isayensi, tekuchumana, tekwakha kanye netemathematika) etikolweni letizimele kanye nakuletinye tindzawo.
Luhlolo lolwentiwe liKhomishani leMisebenti neLwati lase-UK nga-2014 lwaveta kutsi 17% wetizatfu letentiwa tisebenti kutsi tikhatsateke ngekugcwalisa imisebenti, tibangelwa kutsi tisengakwati kukhuluma lulwimi.
Ngako-ke, emakhono elulwimi aya ngekuba matima kakhulu kute alungiselele bantfu labasha imisebenti yabo esikhatsini lesitako.
Njengobe ematfuba emisebenti ledzinga tilwimi etulu, emakhono lafanako abalulekile emhlabeni lowemukelwa kabanti.
Kungakhatsaliseki kutsi umuntfu ukhetsa umsebenti muni, nangabe afundza lulwimi lwesibili, ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi utawutfola inzuzo lenkhulu ngekwenta njalo.
Kucondza bantfu labavela kulamanye emave kutawenta umuntfu losebentisa tilwimi letinyenti abe ngetulu kwalabanye.
Ngekusho kweluhlolo lwe-YouGov lolwentiwe nga-2013 lolwentiwa e-UK, lolwentiwe kubantfu labadzala labangetulu kwa-4 000 bantfu, emaphesenti langu-75 bekangakwati kukhuluma lulwimi lwasemakhaya kahle kute akhulume, kantsi siFrench bekulona kuphela lulwimi lolwakhulunywa bantfu labangaba ngu-15%.
Kungako kubalulekile kutsi bantfwana banake kufundziswa kwetilwimi.
Kwati tilwimi letinyenti, ikakhulukati letisebuchwephesheni lobusaphucuka, kutawenta bantfwana babe nelitfuba lelihle lekutfola umsebenti lonenjongo.
Esikolweni saseScotland, tonkhe tilwimi letifundziswayo tihlukile.
Letinye tikolo titawufundzisa ngetilwimi letisemtsetfweni, kantsi letinye titawufundzisa ngetilwimi letitsatfwa njengetintfo letibalulekile e-UK uma sibheka emuva nga-2020, njengesiMandarin noma siJapan.
Nobe ngabe yini umntfwana wakho lafuna kuyitfola, kuletinye tikolwa letitimele, kutawuba netilwimi letinyenti tekukhetsa ngato, futsi bantfu labafundzisako batawuba bacwepheshe.
Tikolwa letitimele taseScotland titinikele ekuhlinzekeni indzawo yekufundza letawulungisa bantfwana futsi ibaphe emakhono ladzingekako kute baphumelele, kungakhatsaliseki kutsi kutakwentekani esikhatsini lesitako.
Kulomkhakha wemabhizinisi wemhlaba wonkhe, angeke kukhonjwe kutsi tilwimi tisasebenta kakhulu esikhatsini lesitako, ngako-ke kufanele tibonakale emfundvweni.
Ecinisweni, tilwimi talamuhla kufanele tibhekwe "njengemakhono ekuchumana emhlabeni wonkhe".
Tikolwa letitimele titawuchubeka nekuniketa bantfu labasha baseScotland lokuhle, kwehlukahlukana kanye nekucondza.
Kufanele kutsi sente lokuhle.
