Mengameli Donald Trump uvula umhlangano wekukhetfwa ngalobubusuku eWheeling, West Virginia.
Loku kutawuba kwekucala kwemihlangano yaTrump lehleliwe kuleliviki lelitako, lefaka ekhatsi imikhumbi etindzaweni letihle kufaka ekhatsi iTennessee neMississippi.
Ngekubekwa licala lelisemtsetfweni lokulindzelekile kutsi lihlale licinisekile, Trump uhlose kwakha kusekelwa kwekukhetfwa kwesibili njengobe emaRiphabhulikhi asengozini yekulahlekelwa ligunya leKhomishani uma kuvota ngaNovemba.
Utawubukana nini naTrump eWest Virginia lamuhla ebusuku futsi umuntfu ubuka njani ku-inthanethi?
Umhlangano waTrump eWheeling, eNtshonalanga Virginia, uhlelelwe kutsi ufike kusihlwa ngeSontfo, mhlaka 29 Septemba 2018.
Ngephansi kwaloku, ungabukela umhlangano waTrump eWest Virginia ngekusebentisa i-live.
Trump utawucaphela emacala latawubekwa kuleliviki eNkantolo lePhakeme, Brett Kavanaugh, lowatfola kutsi uyangetfusa ngetinsolo tekutiphatsa kabi ngekwelicansi, ngelivoti lelingalindzelekile lekucinisekisa lelibekelwe eceleni liviki linye njengobe i-FBI iphenya.
Kodvwa injongo lenkhulu yaloku kuhlangana lokunyenti kutsi kusite emaRiphabhulikhi lasembili elukhetfweni lolumatima lwangaNovemba.
Umkhankaso waMengameli Trump utsi lemibutfo lesihlanu letawubanjwa kuleliviki lelitako ihlose "kuvakashela emavolontiya kanye nebasekeli ngesikhatsi emaRiphabhulikhi etama kuvikela nekukhulisa linani lawo lelisetulu laseSenate naseNdlini yeTindlu", kusho iReuters.
"Kubusa kweKhomishani kubaluleke kakhulu eluhlelweni lwakhe lwekwenta kutsi umengameli ahambe aye emaveni lamanyenti njengobe kungenteka nasifika ngesikhatsi semkhankhaso lesimatima", kusho sikhulumi semkhankhaso waTrump, lesasila kutsi sitsiwe.
Umbutfo walobubusuku, lobuhlelwe kutsi ubambe inkhosi eWestbanco Arena eWheeling, utawutsatsa bantfu "bavela e-Ohio nasePennsylvania futsi utawutsatfwa ngemabiko ePittsburgh", ngekusho kwe-West Virginia Metro News.
NgeMgcibelo utawuvakashela eVirginia lese Nshonalanga, lokuyindzawo yakhe yekucala leyayihola ngetulu kwa-40% ngemaphesenti nga-2016.
Trump wetama kusita umcashi weSigungu saVelonkhe waseWest Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, lowehluleka ngekusho kwemaphethini.
"Akusiko kutsi loku bekungumbono lomuhle kuMorrisey kutsi umengameli kufanele eze kute amnike inzuzo", kusho Simon Haeder, losati setembusave e-University of West Virginia, ngekusho kwe-Reuters.
