Ri wacaphuna sitatimende lesihlanganyelwe lesakhishwa nguKim Jong-un naDonald Trump engcungcutfweni yekucala emkhatsini wemengameli waseMelika nemholi waseNyakatfo Korea ngaJune 12 eSingapore ngesikhatsi Kim atsatsa sinyatselo sekusebenta "ekubhujiswa kwetibhamu letingu-nuclear eKorea" ngesikhatsi Trump etsembisa kutfola ticinisekiso tekuphepha kweNyakatfo Korea.
INyakatho Korea ifuna kuphela ngelizinga lelisetulu kweMphi YaseKorea ya-1950-53, kodvwa i-United States yatsi iPyongyang kufanele icale ngekunikela ngetibhamu tayo letisisekelo.
I-Washington iphindze yaphikisa ticelo tekunciphisa tihibe letisetjentiswa ngemave emhlaba ku-North Korea.
Ri watsi: "EmaMelika agcizelela 'kubhujiswa kwetibhamu letingu-nuclear kucala' futsi asebentisa emandla lamanyenti ngekucinisa tihibe kute kufinyelelwe injongo yawo ngendlela lecinile, futsi aze aphikisane 'nekumenyetelwa kwekuphela kwemphi.'
"Lemibono yekutsi tijeziso tingasenta sigucuke ingumcabango webantfu labangati lutfo ngatsi.
Kodvwa inkinga kutsi kuciniswa kwetibopho kucinisa kungetsembeki kwetfu".
Ri akazange asho lutfo mayelana netinhlelo teNgcungcutsela yesibili yaKim naTrump, leyaboniswa ngumholi waseMelika ku-United Nations ekucaleni kwaleliviki.
Esikhundleni saloko, waveta imihlangano lemitsatfu leyenteka emkhatsini waKim nemholi waseNingizimu Korea, Moon Jae-in, etinyangeni letisihlanu letengcile, futsi wengeta watsi: "Kube inkantolo lemayelana nekubhujiswa kwetintfo letingu-nuclear beyingasiyo i-US, beyingeke ifinyelele kuleso sigaba".
