Kulomnyaka, e-UN, Trump, lowasongela "kubhubhisa" i-North Korea "ngokuphelele" kulomnyaka lophelile, wancoma Kim ngekukhutsateka kwakhe ngekwenta tinyatselo tekwehlisa tikhali, kodvwa watsi kusekunemsebenti lomnyenti lokufanele wentiwe futsi tijeziso kufanele tihlale tihleli kuze kube sikhatsi lapho i-North Korea ibhubhisa khona tikhali te-nuclear.
NgaLwesitsatfu, Trump watsi ute sikhatsi sekwenta njalo, watsi "Akunandzaba kutsi kutsatsa iminyaka lemibili, iminyaka lemitsatfu nobe tinyanga letisihlanu".
I-China ne-Russia bacabanga kutsi i-UN Security Council kufanele ibeke Pyongyang sikweleti ngetento tato.
Nobe kunjalo, uMengameli we-United States, Mike Pompeo, watsi ku-UN Security Council ngeLesihlanu: "Kuciniswa kwetibopho te-UN kufanele kuchubeke ngekutimisela futsi ngaphandle kwekuphelelwa ngemandla kudzimate kube ngulapho sicedza tonkhe tikhali letingu-nuclear ngalokuphelele, lokugcina, lokucinisekisiwe".
Kusukela nga-2006, i-UNSC yavumelanisa emandla ekucinisa kubekwa kwebantfu baseNyakatfo Korea, kute itfole imali yekwesekela tinhlelo te-nuclear kanye netemikhono yemabhalisi ePyongyang.
