Bafundzi baseHarvard bafundza ngekuphumula lokwenele
Lencwadzi lensha yaHarvard University kulomnyaka itfola bonkhe bafundzi bayo labasebasha kutsi balale kakhulu, kute babhekane nemasiko lamakhulu ekutadisha ngekuhlanganyela 'emihlanganweni' lelawulwa ngekhofi.
Sati semfundvo satfola kutsi bafundzi basemanyuvesi lamanyenti laphakeme emhlabeni bavame kungati kahle tintfo letibalulekile tekutiphatsa.
Charles Czeisler, longuphrofesa wetekwelapha ngekulala eHavard Medical School kanye nalonguchwepheshe weSibhedlela seBrigham kanye neSibhedlela SaBafati, wakha lenchubo, lekholelwa kutsi iyintfo yekucala kuleyo ndlela eMelika.
Waphefumulelwa kutsi acale lenchubo ngemuva kwekuniketa inkhulumo lemayelana nemiphumela yekungalali ekufundzeni.
"Ekupheleni kwalomhlangano, lenye intfombatana yeta kimi yatsi: 'Kungani bangitjela loko nyalo, ngesikhatsi sengineminyaka lesihlanu?'
Watsi kute lowase wamtjela kutsi kulala kubaluleke kangakanani - lokwamangalisa kakhulu,' wachazela The Telegraph.
Lencwadzi, leyacalwa kulomnyaka, ichaza timiso tekutsi imphilo lenhle yekulala ingasita njani bafundzi kutsi babe nemphumelelo emfundvweni kanye nasetincumeni tabo temidlalo, kanye nekutsi ingakwenta njani kutsi babe ncono.
Paul Barreira, longuphrofesa wetemphilo yengcondvo eHavard Medical School kanye nemcondzisi lophetse etemphilo kuleyunivesithi, watsi leyunivesithi yancuma kusebentisa loluhlelo ngemuva kwekubona kutsi bafundzi bebangaphumeleli kakhulu ekulala evikini.
Lencwadzi leyiminyaka lengu-1 000 ifaka ekhatsi imisebenti lelandzelanako.
Kulenye indzawo, kunesitfombe salendlu yekulala lapho bafundzi kufanele bacoce khona etikomitfombo yekhofi, emakhethini, emabhuzu kanye netincwadzi kute batfole kwatiswa ngemiphumela yekwehlisa umtimba kanye nekukhanya kanye nendlela umtimba longcolile lowentiwa ngayo nawungakwati kulala kanye nekubaluleka kwekulala.
Kulenye incenye, labatsintsekako batjelwa kutsi kungalali sikhatsi lesidze kungakwenta ube matima kuhlushwa sifo senhlitiyo, sifo sekushaywa ngumtimba, kucindzeteleka kanye nemdlavuza.
Ibalazwe lesemakhaya, lelineligama lelitsintsekako, likhutsata labahlanganyeli kutsi bacabange ngemalanga abo.
"Siyabona kutsi loko angeke kushintje indlela labafundza ngayo ngekushesha.
Kodvwa siyakholwa kutsi banemalungelo ekwati - njengobe nawe unemalungelo ekwati kutsi kunjani kuphila nangabe ukhetsa kubhema,' kwengeta Prof. Czeisler.
Watsi: "Lendzaba isolo ikhona, futsi itfolakala nangesikhatsi semnyaka".
Watsi kuciniseka kutsi ulala kahle kufanele kube 'sikhwama lesiyimfihlo' semfundzi sekugwema kucindzeteleka, kukhatsateka kanye nekukhatsateka - ngisho nekugwema kutibamba, ngobe kungadli kahle kubeka ingcondvo endzaweni yekudla, lokwenta utive ulambile ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi.
