Umdlandla uvakala shengatsi ubhekiswe kubantfwana kunebantfu labadzala, futsi kimi, kuhlupheka kwaJohnny English akusiyo intfo lenkhulu futsi kugxile kakhulu kunemahlaya a-Atkinson labekahlelwa bantfu labamnyama.
