Lona ngumlayeto wekugcina waNdvunankhulu lonelunya futsi lohluphekako, lovele aphila ngekuwa kwepolitiki: Emma Thomspson wenta konkhe lokusemandleni akhe kutsi abambisane nalomlingisi longumntfwana Theresa May kodvwa kuncane kakhulu lokumele kusetjentiswe.
Beluleki bakhe betekuvikela bantfu bemhlaba bamtjela kutsi njengobe tonkhe tinhloli letisebentako tisengotini, kufanele abite umuntfu kutsi atsatse umhlalaphansi.
Loku kusho kutsi Johnny English yena, lohluphekako, nyalo losebenta njengothishela kulesinye sikhungo lesihle, kepha lofundzisa ngetintfo letingapheli kutsi angaba njani sitfunywa semfihlo, kunemahlaya lajabulisako lapha lapho English ahambisa sikolwa sekusebenta ngebuphekula.
