English naBough bacala luhambo lwabo lwekutibalekela lokuhlekisako: betimphunga batishisa indzawo yekudlela yaseFrance, baletsa ingoti ngesikhatsi batengiswa ngekushushumbisa emkhombeni we-Volta; kantsi English ucala kukhatsateka ngesikhatsi etama kusebentisa intfo letsite ye-virtual reality kute atfole kucondza kwangekhatsi endlini yaVolta.
