Ummeli waseMelika usola iChina ngekuhlukunyetwa 'ngekuhlonishwa kwetindzaba letitsite'
Ngemuva kweliviki liphephandaba laseChina lelisemtsetfweni lishicilele sikhangiso semakhasi lamane ephephandzabeni laseMelika lelisho ngetinzuzo letihlanganyelwe tekutsengiselana kwemave aseMelika nemave aseChina, ummeli waseMelika eChina waseBeijing wamangalela ngekutsi umshini wekuhambisa tindzaba waseMelika usetjentiswe kute usakateke.
Mengameli waseMelika Donald Trump, wabhekisela ku-China Daily's payroll last Wednesday ku-Des Moines Register  liphephandaba lelibaluleke kakhulu e-Iowa  ngemuva kwekusola iChina ngekungenelela elukhetfweni lwe-US Congress ngaNovember 6, solo lesiphika kutsi iChina iyasilahla.
Kubekwa licala nguTrump lekutsi iBeijing iyazama kungenelela lukhetfo lwaseMelika, kwafaka ekhatsi loko lokushiwo tikhulu taseMelika kuReuters kutsi "kucala lokusha emkhankasweni weWashington wekucindzetela iChina".
Nanobe kuyinto levamile kutsi bohulumende bakwamanye emave babeke tikhangiso tekutfutfukisa kutengiselwano, eBeijing naseWashington, emave lamabili angene emphini yekutsengiselana lokunyenti, lokwenta kutsi bafanise tindleko temali yekungenisa kwemali.
Timali tekuphindzisela tase China ekucaleni kwemphi yetekuhweba betibekelwe kuhlasela batsengisi labavela etiveni letifana ne-Iowa, letisekela iRiphabhulikhi yaTrump, kusho tati tase China netaseMelika.
Terry Branstad, longummeli waseMelika eChina kanye naLushawulo Lweminyaka Lwekusebenta Lwase-Iowa, longumtsengisi lomkhulu wetintfo tekulima eChina, watsi iBeijing ilimaza tisebenti taseMelika, balimi kanye netimboni.
China, kubhala Branstad encwadzini yeSontfo letsi Des Moines Register, "ngekunyakata kwetfulwa kwetikhangiso tekutishumayela ngekusebentisa inkhululeko yetfu".
Branstad wabhala watsi: "Ngekusakata inkhulumo yabo, hulumende waseChina ubamba emasiko laseMelika ekuba nenkhululeko yekukhuluma kanye nekusakata ngekubhala sikhangiso lesikhokhelwako ku-Des Moines Register.
Wabhala: "Ngekuphambene naloko, umuntfu utawutfola emavi lalinganiselwe laphambukako etincwadzini letisemgwacweni lapha eBeijing, futsi angeke abone nobe nguyiphi indlela leliciniso lebonakalako yemibono leyehlukene bantfu baseChina labayibukene nalomnotfo lohluphekako waseChina, nangabe umsakato ulawulwa yiCPC".
Wengeta watsi "lelinye lemagazini labaluleke kakhulu eChina lacela kutsi liphume", kodvwa akazange asho kutsi nguliphi.
