Umuntfu lowasungula i-Internet uhlele kusungula i-Internet lensha kute i-Google ne-Facebook batibambe
Tim Berners-Lee, losungula i-World Wide Web, usungula ibhizinisi lelisungula inkampani lefuna kuncintisana ne-Facebook, Amazon ne-Google.
Umsebenti lomusha walendvodza leyengumuntfu lonebuchwepheshe, i-Inrupt, yinkampani leyakha ku-Berners-Lee's open source platform, i-Solid.
Solid ivumela basebentisi kutsi bakhetse lapho idatha yabo igcinwa khona nekutsi bobani bantfu labavunyelwe kufinyelela kulolwati.
