Umcondvo we Inrupt, ngekusho kwaHUB John Bruce, yinkampani kutsi itfole tinsita, tinchubo kanye nemakhono lafanele kute kusite kwenta iSolid itfolakale kubo bonkhe bantfu.
Lenkampani ihlanganisa Berners-Lee, Bruce, ipulatifomu yekuphepha leyatsengwa yi-IBM, bacashi labasebenta ngekusebenta kulomsebenti kanye nemphakatsi webantfu labatinikele ngekubhala ema-code.
Kusukela kuleliviki, bacashi betikhungo letisebenta emhlabeni wonkhe batawukhona kutfutfukisa tinhlelo tabo tekusebentisa emandla abo ngekusebentisa emathulusi latfolakala ku-Inrupt website.
Berners-Lee utsi yena nelicembu lakhe abakhulumi "ne-Facebook ne-Google ngekwetfulwa kwenguquko jikelele, lapho tonkhe tinhlobo tabo temabhizinisi tiphendvuke ngalokuphelele.
"Asiceli imvume yabo".
