Umkhumbi Wemphi WaseJalimane Lomusha Waphindze Wahlehliswa
Umkhumbi lomusha wema-Frigate aseJalimane bewungahle usebente nga-2014 kute utsatse sikhundla sekufaka timphahla letindzala teMphi YeMashi, kodvwa angeke ube khona kuze kube ngumnyaka lotako, ngenca yetintfo letingahambi kahle kanye netindleko letindzako, kusho abeve basekhaya.
Kufakwa kwe-Rheinland-Pfalz, umkhumbi lomkhulu wetincola letinsha letingu-Baden-Wuerttemberg, sekubekiwe kuze kube yingciphekwane yekucala yemnyaka wa-2019, ngekusho kwe-Zeit, lokusho sikhulumi semphakatsi.
Lomkhumbi bekufanele ujoyine i-Navy ngemnyaka wa-2014, kodvwa tinkinga tekutfumela titfunywa ngemuva kwekutfumela titfunywa tawo, talimata likusasa lalomsebenti lobalulekile.
Letitfo letine letingu-Baden-Wuerttemberg letatfunyelwa yi-Navy ngemnyaka wa 2007 titawufaka esikhundleni setincola letingu-Bremen.
Kucondzene kutsi batawuba nebutfo lobunemandla, emabhomu ekuhlasela kanye nemishini yekulwa netikepe kanye netintfo letingabonakali letifana ne-radar, i-infrared kanye netincwadzi letisayinwe ngemsindvo.
Letinye tintfo letibalulekile tifaka ekhatsi sikhatsi lesidze sekugcinwa  kutawuba nemandla ekutsi kutfunyelwe ema-freighters lamasha kuze kuphele iminyaka lemibili angekho ekhaya.
Kodvwa kuchubeka kwekubambezeleka kusho kutsi timphahla letisetulu letitawenta kutsi iJalimane ikhone kutfola emandla phesheya kwemhlaba titawuphelelwa sikhatsi ngesikhatsi tisebenta, kubita libito lelitsi The Zeit.
Lendzawo lebeyiyinkinga ya-F125 yacala kugadla ngemnyaka lophelile ngesikhatsi i-German Fleet ivele yala kusebentisa lomkhumbi futsi yawubuyisela eBlohm & Voss, eHamburg.
Loku bekungesikhatsi sekucala kutsi Umkhumbi Wemkhumbi ubuyisele umkhumbi kumakhi wemkhumbi ngemuva kwekutfunyelwa.
Tizatfu tekutfunyelwa kwemkhumbi emuva atiwa kahle, kodvwa imphakatsi yaseJalimane itsi "linyenti lemasotja lasebenta ngemishini kanye netintfo letingakhi" letiveta kutsi umkhumbi awusebenti nangabe usetjentiswa ngemkhankhaso.
Tintfo letiyinkinga letiphatselene nemsebenti wetehlakalo letiphatselene netehlakalo letenteka emnyakeni lowengcile, tibalulekile ngobe tikhumbi letisebenta eBaden-Wuerttemberg titawuba nemahhashi lacishe abe ngu-120 kuphela labatawenta umsebenti wekusebenta emantini lamadzala aseBremen.
Waphindze watfola kutsi lomkhumbi unesisindvo lesinyenti, lokwenta kutsi umsebenti wakhe unciphe kakhulu futsi kunciphise likhono leLwandle lekwenta tintfo letingahle tenteke esikhatsini lesitako.
Letitoni letingu-7.000 "Rheinland-Pfalz" ticatjangwa kutsi tikhulule kabili kunetintfo letatisetjentiswa ngemaJalimane ngesikhatsi seMphi Yelive Yesibili.
Ngaphandle kwekubekwa kwetintfo letingaphili kahle, kubekwa kwemali kulo lonkhe loluhlelo, lokufaka ekhatsi kuceceshwa kwemasotja, nako kwaba yintfo lebalulekile.
Kubonakala shengatsi lemali seyifinyelele ku-€3.1 billion (kuya ku-€3.6 billion) lengetulu kwa-€2.2 billion lebeyiyivele ivele.
Tinkinga letatfolwa nguletinsha temikhumbi letinsha tiyabonakala ikakhulukati ngenca yeticwayiso letenteka muva kutsi emandla emkhumbi waseJalimane ayaceka.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, Hans-Peter Bartels, longumholi welikomidi lekuvikela lesigungu salelive laseJalimane, wavuma kutsi "tintfo letingahle tihanjiswe nguLuphiko lwetfu Letemikhumbi tiye tacala kulahleka".
Ummeli walelibutfo watsi lendzaba seyiya ngekuya iba mibi njengobe imikhumbi lendzala ingasebenti, kodvwa kute imikhumbi leyayitawusebenta esikhundleni sayo.
Wakhala ngekutsi kute umuntfu lowahamba ngeBaden-Wuerttemberg lobekafanele kutsi ayewujoyina leLwandle.
I-National Trust ilalela imfihlo yetimphungutja
Lucwalingo lolusha lolwentiwa endzaweni yaseScotland lolusekelwe etulu kuleyo ndzawo, lufuna kukhombisa indlela emabhokhwe lasebentisa ngayo indzawo lapho afuna khona kudla.
Letifundvo titakwetsemba kutsi titakukhanyisela indlela letigucuka ngayo tilwane letiphilako futsi tisitise ekucondziseni imisebenti yekulondvolota esikhatsini lesitako.
Lolucwaningo lolwentiwe bososayensi ku-National Trust for Scotland lutawuchubeka neluhlelo loluhlobene neluhlelo loluhlobene lwetinyoni letincane kanye netinyoni letinsundvu letincane letingu-Langor neDaubenton e-Invereve Gardens leseWester Ross.
Tinsimbi tekubhala titobekwa etindzaweni letibalulekile endzaweni kute tihlole imisebenti yemagundvwane ngesikhatsi sonkhe.
Basebenti be-NHS kanye netisebenti letitfunywe ngekutiphilisa batawuphindze basebentise tinhlelo tekufundza ngetinsita letisetjentiswa ngetandla.
Kuhlolisisa konkhe lokufundvwa ngulowo nalowo mfundzi kutawubuka kutsi timphungutja tiyakhala nini futsi tiphi letibamba emagama.
Ibalazwe lelikhombisa indzawo yekuhlala kanye nemibiko kutawubese kuhlanganiswa kute kuvele sitfombe lesinemininingwane lesinemave lesinemkhawulo wekutiphatsa kwabo.
Rob Dewar, longumeluleki wetekuvikela imvelo ku-NTS, unethemba lekutsi imiphumela itawukhombisa kutsi nguyiphi indzawo yekuhlala lebonakala ibaluleke kakhulu kulenhlobo kanye nekutsi isetjentiswa njani nguleyo naleyo ndzawo.
Lolwati lutawusita ekuboneni tinzuzo tekuphatsa tindzawo tekuhlala, njengekwakha emadlelo kanye nekuphatsa kahle emahlathi etinhlavu kanye naletinye tilwane letihlobene nato.
Tindlulamitsi taseScotland kanye naletinye tindzawo tase-UK tiye tahla kakhulu kuleminyaka lelikhulu leyengcile.
Tisetingotini tekwakha kanye nekutfutfukiswa kwemhlaba lokutsintsa indzawo yekuhlala kanye nekulahleka kwetindzawo tekuhlala.
Ema-wind turbines kanye nemandla emandla angaphindze abe yingoti, kanye neliphepha lelibhaliwe kanye nekwelashwa kwemakhemikhali kwetintfo tekwakha kanye nekuhlaselwa ngemakati.
Timphungane atiboni mbamba.
Kodvwa ngenca yemisebenti yabo yekutingela ebusuku, tindlebe tabo tiyasebenta kwendlula emehlo abo ekubambeni kudla.
Basebentisa indlela lebucayi yekubonisa umoya kanye netintfo letibavimbelako endleleni.
I-NTS, lebhekele tindzawo letingetulu kwa-270 letinemlandvo, tingadze letingu-38 letinkhulu kanye nemhlaba longemahekitha langu-76.000 eveni lonkhe, ibukene kakhulu nemavukutfu.
Linelwati loluphelele lwebachwepheshe labalishumi labavame kuhlolwa, kuhlolwa kwekulala kanye nekusindziswa.
LeNhlangano yaze yakha indzawo yekucala futsi yekuphela yekugcina yetinhlavu taseScotland, eThreave Estate eDumfries naseGalloway, lapho kuhlala khona tinhlavu tetinhlavu letisiphohlongo kuletilishumi taseScotland.
Umphatsi wetakhiwo David Thompson utsi indzawo yabo iyintfo lekahle kubo.
Watsi: "Lapha eThreave sinelikhaya lelihle kakhulu letimphungane.
"Sine takhiwo takadzeni, tihlahla letinyenti temahhashi kanye netindzawo letinhle.
Kodvwa kunalokunyenti lokungazange sekwatiwe ngemabhodlo, ngako umsebenti lesiwentako lapha nakuletinye tindzawo usisita kutsi sikucondze kahle loko lokudzingekako kute aphumelele".
Uphindze agcizelele kubaluleka kwekusesha emagundvwane ngaphambi kwekugcina emakhaya ngobe kungenteka kutsi kubhujiswa lokungafuneki kwendzawo yinye kungabulala tilwane letinsikati letingu-400 kanye netinswane, futsi kubulale bantfu labanyenti.
Timphungutja tivikelekile futsi akukafaneli kutibulala, kutiphazamisa, kutivimbela nobe kucekela phansi tindzawo tato tekulala.
Elisabeth Ferrell, losisebenti saseScotland lesisebenta kuBat Conservation Trust, wakhutsata bantfu kutsi bete batewusita.
Watsi: "Sisachubeka nekufundza lokunyenti ngetimphungutja tetfu futsi tilwane tetfu letinyenti atiwati kutsi tinjani.
Ronaldo uvala emacala ekudlwengula ngesikhatsi bammeli balungiselela kumangalela bomagazini baseJalimane
Cristiano Ronaldo walahla emacala ekudlwengula labekangeke abekwe wona ngekutsi "atindzaba letingemanga" watsi bantfu "bafuna kutiphakamisa" ngekusebentisa ligama lakhe.
Emagqwetha akhe alungele kumangalela bomagazini waseJalimane lobitwa ngekutsi yiDer Spiegel, lobekafaka leto tizatfu.
Lomdlali wasePortugal kanye neJuventus, usolwa ngekudlwengula umfati waseMelika libito lakhe lokunguKathryn Mayorga ehhotela laseLas Vegas nga-2009.
Kubikwa kutsi wamkhokhela imali lengu-R375 000 kute angavumeli kutsi kwenteke loko, iDer Spiegel yabika ngaLesihlanu.
Ngemuva kwekushicilelwa kwelividiyo lelibukene netinsayeya letingu-142 million, Ronaldo loneminyaka lengu-33 budzala, wavala lomlayeto ngekutsi "utindzaba letingemanga".
"Cha, cha, cha, cha, cha.
Loku lokwashiwo ngubo lamuhla, tindzaba letingemanga", kwasho lomphumelele weBallon dOr tikhatsi letisihlanu.
"Bafuna kutiphakamisa ngekusebentisa ligama lami.
Loku kuvamile.
Bafuna kudvumisa bantfu ngekutsiwa ligama lami, kodvwa loko kuyincenye yaloko.
Ngingumuntfu lojabulako futsi konkhe kuhamba kahle", kwengeta lomdlali amomotheka.
Ummeli waRonaldo usalungiselela kulahla iDer Spiegel ngalokushiwo, labakuchaza ngekutsi "kukhuluma ngekungetsembeki ngekungetsembeki".
Ummeli Christian Schertz watsi lomdlali utawufuna inhlawulo "ngekulimala ngekwemtsetfo nobe ngabe ngukuphi lokungaba ngulokutsite lokukhombisa kutsi uphetse kabi, lokungenteka kutsi ngulokunye kwephulwa kwemalungelo ebantfu labatsite lokukhulu kakhulu eminyakeni leyendlulile".
Lesento lesimangaliswako sitsi senzeka ngaJune 2009 ku-Palm's Hotel and Casino eLas Vegas.
Ngemuva kwekuhlangana ehhotela, Ronaldo naMaurga basuke baya ekamelweni lemdlali, lapho bekungenteka khona amdlwengule, ngekusho kwemiculu leyatfulwa enkantolo yesifundza saseClark County, eNevada.
Mayorga utsi Ronaldo wawela phansi ngemuva kwalesigameko, watsi "ngemaphesenti langema-99"  "umuntfu lolungile" lowashiywa "ngemaphesenti lalishumi".
Letincwadzi titsi Ronaldo wacinisekisa kutsi labantfu labashadene bebenta budlelwane bebungoti, kodvwa loko bekungemcondvo lofanako.
Mayorga uphindze atsi waya emaphoyiseni futsi wacela kutsi atsatfwe titfombe tekulimala kwakhe esibhedlela, kodvwa wavuma kucedza inkantolo ngobe "abesaba kuphindziselwa" futsi bekakhatsateke ngekutsi "utawutfotjiswa embikwebantfu".
Lomuntfu loneminyaka lengu-34 utsi ufuna kuphendvula simo ngobe usatfola buhlungu ngenca yaloko lokushiwo ngulesento.
Ronaldo bekasetawujoyina iReal Madrid aseManchester United ngesikhatsi lesento lesimangalisako, futsi wabhalisa ku-Juve, inkhosi yase-Italy, ngesivumelwano lesingu-€100 million kulelihlobo.
Brexit: UK 'itawuzisola phakadze' uma ikhokha timoto
I-UK 'itawuzisola phakadze' uma ilahlekelwa sitfunti sayo njengenhloko yemhlaba yetemoto ngemuva kwe-Brexit, kusho Mengameli weTimboni Greg Clark.
Wengeta watsi "kuyamangalisa" kutsi i-Toyota yase-UK itjele BBC kutsi uma i-UK ishiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano, itawuyekela kwesikhashana kukhicita e-Burnaston, dvute ne-Derby.
"Sidzinga sivumelwane", kwasho Mnu. Clark.
Umkhicito wetimoto waseJapan utsi umtselela wekubambezeleka kwemincele uma ngabe kuvele "kute sivumelwano" se-Brexit ungahle uletsele bantfu imisebenti.
Lesitjalo saseBurnaston lesakhiwa yiToyota's Auris ne-Avensis sakha tigidzi letingu-150,000 temoto emnyakeni lophelile, futsi 90% wato watfunyelwa kulamanye emave aseYurophu.
Marvin Cooke, umcondzisi lophetse weToyota eBurnaston watsi: "Ngibona shengatsi uma ngabe i-UK ishiya i-EU ekupheleni kwaMarch, sitawucedza kukhicita efektri yetfu".
Labanye bakhiciti bemoto base-UK, lokufaka ekhatsi i-Honda, i-BMW kanye ne-Jaguar Land Rover, bakhuluma ngekwesatjiswa kwekushiya EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano nekutsi kutengiswa kwemikhawulo yeminyango kutawusebenta njani.
Sibonelo saloko kutsi, iBMW itsi itawuvala sitjalo sayo se-Mini e-Oxford inyanga yinye ngemuva kwe-Brexit.
Lokukhatsateka lokukhulu kubangelwa nguloko lokushiwo tikhungo tekuphakela timphahla tekusebenta uma ngabe i-Brexit ingekho.
Umgca wekukhicita weToyota usebenta ngekusebenta "ngesikhatsi" lokutsiwa, ngetincenye letitfolakalako letifika njalo ngemizuzu lengu-37 kusuka kuboneleli base-UK nase-EU, tekukhicita timoto letentelwe umyalelo.
Uma ngabe i-UK ishiya i-EU ingakwati kuhlangabetana netimo letibucayi ngemhlaka 29 Mashi, kungahle kube nekuphazamiseka kwemngcele lokungaholela ekutseni kube nekwephuta kanye nekushoda kwetintfo tekwakha.
Leyo nkampani itsi ngeke yente kutsi iToyota igcine tintfo letingaba ngetulu kwelilanga linye eDerbyshire, ngako-ke, kukhicita kutawuvalwa.
Clark utsi luhlelo lwaTheresa May lwe-Chequers lwekuhlanganyela esikhatsini lesitako ne-EU "luyehliswe kahle kute kugwenywe loko kuhlolwa kwemncele".
"Sidzinga sivumelwane. Sifuna sivumelwane lesikahle, njengobe ngitsi, lesingasenta singanaki kuphela impumelelo lesinayo nyalo, kodvwa lesingasenta sisitsatse lesikhatsi", washo kulenhlelo ya-BBC Radio 4's Today.
"Tinkhomba letisuka hhayi kuToyota kuphela, kodvwa nakuletinye takhi, kutsi sidzinga kakhulu kuchubeka naloko lokwasenta saba nemphumelelo lenkhulu.
I-Toyota ayikatjeli kutsi kutawutsatsa sikhatsi lesingakanani kuvalwa kwekukhicita, kodvwa yacaphela kutsi ngetindleko letengetiwe, esikhatsini lesidze, kungaba nekuncintisana lokuncane futsi ekugcineni kutawudzinga imisebenti.
Peter Tsouvallaris, losasebenta eBurnaston iminyaka lengu-24 futsi lowenta umsebenti wekubita bantfu kutsi bahlanganyele ku-UNite Union, utsi emalunga ayo akhatsateke kakhulu: "Ngemlandvo wami, uma lemitfwalo iphela, ngeke iphindze ibuye.
Umkhulumeli wahulumende watsi: "Siphakamise luhlelo lolunembile nalolwemukelekako lwekuhlanganyela kwetfu ne-EU esikhatsini lesitako.
Umhlangano waTrump naRosenstein ungahle ubekwe emuva, kusho iWhite House
Umhlangano waDonald Trump lobekahle ubhekene neSekela laMengameli Rod Rosenstein "ungahle ubekelwe eceleni ngesonto" njengobe kuphikisana ngekwetfulwa kwelicala lelikhulu Brett Kavanaugh kuchubeka, kusho iWhite House ngeSontfo.
Rosenstein ubuka umsebenti weMeluleki Lomkhulu weMtsetfo Robert Mueller, lohlolisisa kungenelela kweRussia elukhetfweni, tixhumanisi emkhatsini webantfu labemele Trump neRussia kanye nekucitsa umtsetfo lobungaba khona ngumengameli.
Kungakhatsaliseki kutsi Trump utawuyekela yini umsebenti wakhe, futsi loko kutawubeka kukhululeka kwaMuler engotini, sekuphele tinyanga letinyenti kuhulumende waseWashington avuse tinkhulumo letimbi.
Ekucaleni kwalenyanga, i-New York Times yabika kutsi Rosenstein wacoca ngekutsatsa umlayeto wekucopha kute acophe tinkhulumo naTrump kanye nekucedza umengameli ngekwe-25th Amendment.
Rosenstein waphika lombiko.
Kodvwa ngeMsombuluko lowengcile waya eNdlini yeMhlophe, etindzaweni letitsi utawuyishiya.
Esikhundleni saloko, umhlangano waTrump, lowawuse-United Nations eNew York, wamenyetelwa kutsi utawubanjwa ngeLwesine.
Trump watsi "ngeke akhetse" kulahla Rosenstein, kodvwa lomhlangano wabese uyabekwa kute kugwenywe kuhlangana kwelicala leSenate lapho khona Kavanaugh kanye nalomunye wabesifazane labamsola ngekutiphatsa kabi ngekwelicansi, Dokotela Christine Blasey Ford, bobabili bafakaza.
NgaLesihlanu, Trump wachuba luphenyo lwe-FBI lwemaviki lambalwa lwemacala labhekene naKavanaugh, futsi wahlehlisa livoti leliphelele leSigungu saVelonkhe.
Umengameli waTrump, Sarah Sanders, wavela ku-Fox News ngeSontfo.
