INcwadzi yeNcwadzi yeTemphilo ye-EU lebhalela basebenti be-NHS Scotland ngekwesaba kwe-Brexit
INcwadzi lebhalwe nguLobhala weTemphilo yabhalela basebenti base-EU labasebenta ku-NHS yaseScotland kute bavakalise kubonga kwalelive kanye nesifiso sekuhlala ngemuva kwe-Brexit.
Jeanne Freeman MSP watfumela incwadzi lesinetinombolo letingekho ngaphansi kwetinyanga letisitfupha ngaphambi kwekutsi i-UK iphume e-EU.
Hulumende waseScotland sewuvele utibophetse kutsi utawukhokhela tindleko tekucedza ticelo tekuba sakhamuti se-EU lesisebenta kuhulumende lowehlukanisiwe.
Encwadzini yakhe, Ms. Freeman wabhala: "Ebusika, tinkhulumiswano emkhatsini we-UK ne-EU tekushiya tichubeka, futsi tincumo letibukekako tiyatfolakala kuloluhambo.
Kodvwa hulumende wase-UK uphindze wacinisa tilungiselelo takhe tekuba nesimo lesingase singeneli.
Ngiyati kutsi lesi sikhatsi lesimatima kini nonkhe.
Kungako ngifuna kuphindze ngivete kutsi ngitsatsa malini umnikelo webasebenti ngamunye, kungakhatsaliseki kutsi bavela kuphi.
Bangani betfu labavela kulo lonkhe lelive lase-EU nangetulu, baletsa lwati lolubalulekile kanye nemakhono lacinisa futsi atfutfukise umsebenti wetemphilo, futsi loku kuzuzisa tigulane nemiphakatsi lesiyisebentako.
E-Scotland yikhaya lenu futsi sifisa kutsi nihlale lapha.
Christion Abercrombie uhlinzwa ngekushesha ngemuva kwekulimala enhloko
