Umceceshi lomkhulu waseTennessee State Rod Reed watjela betindzaba kutsi lomonakalo wenteka ngaphambi nje kwekuphumula.
"Wafika eceleni kwemugca futsi wavele wavele wawela lapho", kwasho Reed.
Bacocisheli kanye netisebenti tetekwelapha baniketa Abercrombie umoya-mpilo eceleni kwemgca wekuphumula ngaphambi kwekutsi afakwe etiteni futsi abuyiselwe emuva kute acondziswe.
Sikhulu saseTennessee State satjela Chris Harris wase-WSMV eNashville, Tennessee, kutsi Abercrombie usemkhatsini we-Vanderbilt Medical Center.
Harris wengeta watsi "kusengakenteki lutfo lolucondzile mayelana neluhlobo/bulungiswa balokulimala" futsi Tennessee isetama kutfola kutsi kwenteka nini.
Abercrombie, loseminyakeni lemibili budzala, usemnyakeni wakhe wekucala e-Tennessee State ngemuva kwekushiya i-Illinois.
