Kutamatama Kwemhlaba Kanye Nematsunami E-Indonesia
Bantfu lokungenani labangu-384 babulawa kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kanye ne-tsunami lehlasela lidolobha lase-Indonesia iPalu ngaLesihlanu, kusho tisebenti, futsi lizinga lekufa litawukhula.
Ngekucondzisa, tikhulu tetinsita tetimphango atizange tikwati kutfola lutfo kuDonggala Regency, indzawo lese nyakatfo yePalu lelisedvute kakhulu nemtfombo welitulu lelibanga lelingu-7.5.
Ngemuva kwenhlekelele ePalu, bantfu labangetulu kwa-16 000 baphephile.
Nakhu lokumbalwa lokuncono lokumayelana nePalu neDonggala, esichingini saseSulawesi:
iPalu, iyinhloko-dolobha yesifundza sase Central Sulawesi, lesiseceleni kwelibhande lelibovu elugwini lwasentshonalanga lwesifundza sase Sulawesi, inebantfu labangu 379 800 nga-2017.
Lelidolobha beligubha iminyaka lengema-40 liphila ngesikhatsi kutamatama kwemhlaba kanye ne-tsunami kuhlasela.
Donggala, sifundza lesiseNyakatfo-Ntshonalanga yeSulawesi, sihlanganisa tigodzi letingaba ngemakhilomitha langetulu kwa-300 (timayili) letiseceleni kwelwandle.
Lesigodzi, lesingumkhakha wetekuphatsa ngaphasi kwesifundza, saba nebantfu labangu 299 200 nga-2017.
Kufuywa kwetimfishi kanye nebulimi kuyincenye yekusimama kwemnotfo weSifundza saseCentral Sulawesi, ikakhulukati endzaweni leseceleni kwemfula iDonggala.
Kulima timayini telicineni nako kubalulekile kulesigodzi, kepha kuningi lokugcinwe eMorowali, endzaweni lephambene neSulawesi.
Ngekusho kwe-Indonesia's Disaster Mitigation Agency, iPalu neDonggala betihlaselwe ema-tsunami emahlandla lamanyenti kuleminyaka lengu-100 leyengcile.
Nga-1938, i-tsunami yabulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-200 futsi yabhubhisa emakhulu emakhaya eDonggala.
I-tsunami nayo yashaya iDonggala lese ningizimu nga-1996, yabulala bantfu labasiphohlongo.
I-Indonesia ihlala endzaweni lephakeme kakhulu leyayisemkhathini weLwandle iPacific, futsi ivame kutamatama kakhulu.
Nati letinye tetintfo letenteka emhlabeni letinkhulu kanye netihlaselwa nguletintfo letenteka eminyakeni lembalwa leyendlulile:
2004: Kuzamazama lokukhulu lokwenteka ngasogwini lwasentshonalanga wesifundza sase-Aceh eNingizimu Sumatra, e-Indonesia ngaDecember 26 kwaholela ku-tsunami lehlasela emave langu-14, kwabulala bantfu labangu-226 000 ngasogwini lwe-Indian Ocean, ngetulu kwehhafu kubo e-Aceh.
2005: Lulwimi lwesiSumatra lwahlaselwa kutamatama kwemhlaba lokunyenti ngasentshonalanga yeMarch nakucala kwe-April.
Emakhulukhulu etigidzi bantfu bashona eNias Island, eceleni kwelwandle lwaseSumatra.
2006: I-6.8 yakhukhula iningizimu yeJava, Indonesia yaba sihlala lesinebantfu labanyenti, lokwaholela ku- tsunami lehlasela lwandle loluseNingizimu, yabulala bantfu labalinganiselwa ku-700.
Nga-2009: Kwenteka kugcwala lokukhulu lokungu-7.6 endzaweni ledvutane nelidolobha lase Padang, lelisedolobheni lelikhulu lesifundza sase Western Sumatra.
Bantfu labangetulu kwa-1 100 bafa.
2010: Kwenteka kutamatama lokukhulu lokungu-7.5 lokwabangela kutsi kube ne-tsunami lengemamitha langu-10 ngetulu kwelizinga lelisetulu, lelahlela emadolobha lamanyenti futsi lebulala bantfu labangu-300.
2016: Kuzamazama lokukhulu kwahlasela umbuso wasePidi Jaya e-Aceh kwaholela ekubhujisweni nasekuhlukunyetweni ngesikhatsi bantfu bakhunjutwa ngekubhujiswa kwalelitsunami lebulalako nga-2004.
Loku akuzange kuholele ku-tsunami kuloku, kodvwa kwafa bantfu labangetulu kwa-100 ngenca yekudlidlita kwetakhiwo.
2018: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kuhlasela sihlala sase Lombok, lesinebantfu labangetulu kwa-500, ikakhulukati enyakatfo yalesihlala.
Lomhlaba wabhidlita tinkhulungwane tetakhiwo futsi tigidzi tetivakashi tahlala tingekho.
