Track Palin, indvodzana lendzala yaLobese Governor wase-Alaska kanye naSarah Palin, lobekangumengameli weliphalamende, uboshwe ngekwetfulwa emacala ekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelikhaya.
Palin, loneminyaka lengu-29 budzala, waseWasilla, e-Alaska, uboshwe asolwa ngekubandlulula licala lakhe lekuhlukunyetwa ngekwebudlova basekhaya, kanye nekuphikisa kuboshwa, ngekusho kwembiko lokhishwe ngemhlakaMgcibelo ngemaphoyisa ase-Alaska.
Ngekusho kwemibiko yemaphoyisa, watsatsa lucingo lwemsikati lebekamati ngesikhatsi abita emaphoyisa kute abike lobugebengu lobentiwa.
Palin uboshwe eMat-Su Prejudicial Facility futsi uboshwe ngetimali letingu-$500, kubikwa yi-KTUU.
Watfolakala enkantolo ngaMgcibelo, lapho atsi "abenacala, nakanjani" nakabutwa kutsi yini layenta, kusho inethiwekhi.
Palin ubhekene netigameko letintsatfu tekuphula umtsetfo, lokusho kutsi angahlala ejele iminyaka leminingi futsi aniketwe inhlawulo lengu-R5 000 000.
Uphindze abekwe licala lekuphulwa kwemtsetfo lobitwa ngekutsi yi-B, lokugwetjwa lilanga linye ejele kanye nelicala lelingu-R2 000.
Akusiko kwekucala kutsi Palin afakwe emacaleni ebugebengu.
NgaDisemba 2017, wabekwa licala lekuhlukumeza uyise, Todd Palin.
Make wakhe Sarah Palin wabita emaphoyisa abika kutsi kuhlasela kwakhe kwenteka.
Lelicala lisenkantolo yema-Veterans ase-Alaska.
NgaJanuary 2016, wabekwa licala lekusebentisa kabi emandla ekuphatsa ngekwemndeni, kungenelela ekubikeni ngebugebengu lobentiwa ngekwebudlova basekhaya kanye nekuphatsa sigameko sekuba nesibhamu ngesikhatsi adzakiwe.
Lendvodzakati yakhe yatsi imshaya ebusweni.
